cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting the DMRS type A position to an invalid value '2' will cause configuration errors in the physical layer setup and prevent proper downlink synchronization.
du.explanation_zh: 將 DMRS 類型 A 位置設定為無效值 '2' 會在物理層設定中導致配置錯誤，並阻止正確的下行鏈路同步。
